The SQL query in the [KB|http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRAKB/Issue+Operations+are+Failed+by+the+PK+Violation+of+Database]:
{quote}
update SEQUENCE_VALUE_ITEM SET seq_id = (select max(ID) from jiraissue) + 10 where seq_name='ChangeGroup';
{quote}
Should be referring to the table 'changegroup' not 'jiraissue':
{quote}
update SEQUENCE_VALUE_ITEM SET seq_id = (select max(ID) from changegroup) + 10 where seq_name='ChangeGroup';
{quote}

