It would be nice to add Assignee to the quick search/smart querying syntax.

As of JIRA 4.4.3, Quick Search supports the "my" search term for items assigned to me but it does not expose a method for arbitrarily naming an assignee.
The precedent here is the R: search term added in 4.3 (JRA-15250) to allow searches for me, username or none.
